race.comment: JOHN RAMBO (4) got a mile back before making late ground to finish fifth in $250k Class 6 in the Magic Millions Carnival. Freshened up and gets all the favours from the nice gate so he should have no excuses. GREEN FLY (1) turned in an eye-catcher first-up in the Listed Carrington at Randwick over this distance three weeks ago. Three-time second-up winner who just needs luck from the wide draw to be right in the finish. SUPER DUCK (12) has been safely held in both runs this prep but can improve sharply out to this more suitable distance. FREE CARRY (7) resumes and has great first up credentials. TONNEOFGRIT (9) also in the mix.
